~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : topic                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : topic [<message>/-c]

   This will allow you to set the current topic in the room you are 
   in.  The -c switch allows you to clear the current topic, without 
   having to add a new one.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
